						               													<description>A volley of rockets to the right while you dodge left and 2 enemy walkers are left scattered across the country side. All is going well until a plasma beam knocks out the targeting pod. Gotta deal with the enemy elite on manual.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     * * * * &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Welcome to Weasel-Tech, a solo campaign game of giant anime robot action.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Lead your Strike Force against the enemy forces, engaging swarms of enemy mecha and dangerous elites in deadly combat. Built from the ground up for fast-moving warfare, the features include:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Solo game play from the ground up. All you need is some miniatures and you can start your own game play. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    People wishing to play with friends can use the Dueling mechanics to face off against each other or can take a pilot each and help each other against the enemy army.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Full campaign game including random events, operational progress and character progression.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Your pilots both gain in experience and skill but so does the command staff guiding you on your missions. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Fast playing combat rules inspired by anime mecha shows and comics. No plodding robots here.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Undertake randomly generated missions with random events and side objectives.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Call down reinforcements, supporting fire or other HQ support during battles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Outfit your mechs with weapons and equipment researched during the campaign.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Defeated villains may return to haunt you with upgraded weapons and equipment.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Includes a full Social System, allowing you to follow your pilots and crew as they make friends, get in fights or even fall in love.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Usable with any mech figures you have available (or for that matter many power armor miniatures).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
